---
import { Leaf } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
		<div class="relative">
			<div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-64 h-64 bg-verde-cremoso/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
			<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-['Playfair_Display'] italic text-verde-hueso leading-tight relative">
				Nuestra <span class="text-verde-cremoso">Esencia</span>
			</h2>
			<p class="mt-8 text-xl text-verde-hueso/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
				En <span class="font-bold text-verde-hueso">La Verde Cancún</span>, creemos que la calidad no es negociable. Seleccionamos cada ingrediente pensando en la explosión de sabor de tu paladar.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4 text-verde-cremoso font-bold">
				<Leaf size={32} />
				<span class="uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">100% Orgánico & Local</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="h-64 bg-verde-cremoso/30 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523049673857-d188397b32a0?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Aguacate fresco" />
				</div>
				<div class="h-40 bg-verde-hueso rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center p-6 text-white text-center">
					<p class="font-bold italic">Sabor que enamora</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="pt-12">
				<div class="h-full bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-2 border border-verde-cremoso/10">
					<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559181567-c3190ca9959b?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl" alt="Ingredientes" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>